Copy SONiC image to remote host:
scp sonic-pensando.bin root@10.64.247.103:/tmp/

SSH to remote host:
ssh root@10.64.247.103

Go to /tmp directory:
cd /tmp/

Start HTTP server on port 8080:
python3 -m http.server 8080

Verify SONiC image version:
strings /var/tmp/sonic_image.bin | grep SONiC-OS-internal-202511
